Episode Description

The chef endures a rigorous physical challenge with a group of Royal
Marines before cooking them a low-calorie but full-flavour beef curry.
Politician David Blunkett takes on Gordon in the recipe challenge with
his shepherds pie, and All Saints Melanie Blatt, Nicole Appleton
and their mothers cook a three-course meal for guests including Nicoles
husband Liam Gallagher
